        <h2>Relax, recover, and see if it feels like home.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Respite care at Azalea Estates is a short-term stay, typically 30 days or longer, with access to every service and amenity our long-term residents enjoy. Same staff, same dining room, same wellness programs. No second-class experience.</p>
        <p>We offer respite care for three distinct situations: post-hospital or post-surgical recovery, caregiver respite (giving a family caregiver a well-deserved break), and prospective residents who want to experience the community before committing to a permanent move.</p>
        <p>That last group is worth mentioning: once respite care guests experience our homelike setting and community, they often choose to become residents.</p>
