<!-- THREE USE CASES -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Who Respite Care Is For</span>
      <h2>Three reasons families choose a short stay.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media">
          <img src="/assets/images/personal-training.jpg"
               alt="One-on-one recovery support at Azalea Estates" loading="lazy">
          <div class="feature-card__badge" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon('shield', 15) }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Post-Surgical &amp; Hospital Recovery</h3>
          <p>Recovering from a hip replacement, cardiac event, stroke, or other health episode often requires more support than home allows. Respite care at Azalea Estates provides a safe, supportive environment with on-site licensed nursing, 24/7 staffing, wellness programs, and three nutritious meals daily. Exactly what the recovery process needs.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media">
          <img src="/assets/images/group-of-women-smiling.jpg"
               alt="Residents happy and well cared for at Azalea Estates" loading="lazy">
          <div class="feature-card__badge" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon('users', 15) }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Caregiver Relief</h3>
          <p>Family caregivers do extraordinary, often invisible work. A week or month of respite care gives a primary caregiver the time to rest, travel, or attend to their own health, with the confidence that their loved one is in expert, compassionate hands. Caregiver wellbeing matters too, and we take it seriously.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-card__media">
          <img src="/assets/images/group-dining.jpg"
               alt="Residents enjoying a meal together in the Azalea Estates dining room" loading="lazy">
          <div class="feature-card__badge" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon('leaf', 15) }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card__body">
          <h3>Trial Stay Before Moving</h3>
          <p>Choosing a senior living community is a significant decision. A respite stay lets prospective residents experience the dining room, join activities, meet neighbors, and get a feel for daily life before making any long-term commitment. It&rsquo;s the best possible way to answer the question: &ldquo;Could this feel like home?&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
